data.title: WVAH-TV
data.meta_description: WVAH moved from UHF channel 23 to VHF channel 11 on April 11, 1988, this came 2 years after becoming one of the original charter Fox affiliates on October 9, 1986. This logo was similar used by its sister station WUTV in Buffalo, New York from 1992 to 1993.
